electeerde talen. De teksten worden automatisch vertaald.','Backend / Global / HintSet the translation of this entry as the translation for the selected languages. The texts are translated automatically.'=>'Stel de vertaling van deze invoer in als de vertaling voor de geselecteerde talen. De teksten worden automatisch vertaald.','Backend / Global / Things to know / HeadlineSynchronize <translation-key id="Synchronize-Configuration">Configuration</translation-key> Explained'=>'Uitleg over <translation-key id="Synchronize-Configuration">Configuratie</translation-key> synchroniseren','Backend / Global / Things to know / HeadlineSynchronize <translation-key id="Synchronize-Translation">Translation</translation-key> Explained'=>'Uitleg over <translation-key id="Synchronize-Translation">Vertaling</translation-key> synchroniseren','Backend / License / Alert MessageA valid license is required to use this feature of Borlabs Cookie. <a href="?page=borlabs-cookie-license">Click here</a> to enter your license key, or <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>click here</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to log into your account and purchase a license renewal.'=>'Een geldige licentie is vereist om deze functie van Borlabs Cookie te gebruiken. <a href="?page=borlabs-cookie-license">Klik hier</a> om uw licentiesleutel in te voeren, of <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>klik hier</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> om in te loggen op uw account en een licentieverlenging aan te schaffen.','Backend / License / Alert MessageYour license key is not valid for this version. This version of Borlabs Cookie was released after your license has expired, therefore you have to <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>click here</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to log into your account and purchase a license renewal.'=>'Uw licentiesleutel is niet geldig voor deze versie. Deze versie van Borlabs Cookie is uitgebracht nadat uw licentie is verlopen; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>klik hier</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> om in te loggen op uw account en een licentieverlenging aan te schaffen.','Backend / License / Alert MessagePlease renew your license key to receive updates. <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span>Click here</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to log into your account and purchase a license renewal.'=>'Vernieuw uw licentiesleutel om bijwerkingen te ontvangen. <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span>Klik hier</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> om in te loggen op uw account en een licentieverlenging aan te schaffen.','Backend / License / Alert MessageYour license has expired. This feature is not available with an expired license. <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span>Click here</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to log into your account and purchase a license renewal.'=>'Uw licentie is verlopen. Deze functie is niet beschikbaar met een verlopen licentie. <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span>Klik hier</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span