ice Groups / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. Not available for default <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key>.'=>'Verwijder de <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key>. Dit is niet beschikbaar voor standaard <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Servicegroepen</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>.'=>'Bewerk de <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is inactive and not displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Essential</translation-key>.'=>'De <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key> is inactief en wordt niet getoond in het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key>. Niet beschikbaar voor de <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Essentiële</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageYour configured domain is different from the website domain. The setting may be incorrect and will cause the Dialog to reappear on each page.'=>'Uw geconfigureerde domein is anders dan het websitedomein. Deze instelling kan onjuist zijn, waardoor het dialoogvenster op elke pagina zal worden getoond.','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageYou have enabled <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Do Not Track&quot;</translation-key> in your browser therefore you will not see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> on your website.'=>'U hebt <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Niet tracken&quot;</translation-key> ingeschakeld in uw browser, waardoor u het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key> niet ziet op uw website.','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageIf this option is active, most likely all visits will be counted as "Direct visits" and the origin will be lost. We therefore recommend not to activate this option!'=>'Als dit is ingeschakeld, worden waarschijnlijk alle bezoeken geteld als "directe bezoeken" en gaat de herkomst verloren. We raden daarom aan deze optie niet te activeren!','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageOnly activate this option if you need to reload your page after consent. Less than 1 &#37; of all <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> customers need this option enabled. If you don\'t know if you need this option, you won\'t need it.'=>'Activeer deze optie alleen als u uw pagina opnieuw moet laden na het geven van toestemming. Minder dan 1 &#37; van alle klanten van <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> moeten deze optie hebben ingeschakeld. Als u niet zeker weet of u deze optie nodig hebt, dan hebt u hem waarschijnlijk niet nodig.','Backend / Settings / BreadcrumbSettings'=>'Instellingen','Backend / Settings / LabelAggregate Consents'=>'Toestemmingen samenvoegen','Backend / Settings / LabelAutomatic Domain and Path Detection'=>'Automatische detectie van domeinen en paden','Backend / Settings / Label<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie Status</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Status van Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / LabelDomain'=>'Domein','Backend / Settings / LabelCookie Lifetime in Days'=>'Cookie levenslang in dagen','Backend / Settings / LabelCookie Lifetime in Days - Essential Only'=>'Cookie levenslang in dagen - Alleen Essentiële','Backend / Settings / LabelPath'=>'Pad','Backend / Settings / Label<translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure attribute</translation-key>'=>'<translation-k