ettings / HintSpecify the domain scheme for which the cookie is valid. Example: If you enter <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> the cookie is also valid for subdomains like <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'Geef het domeinschema op waarvoor de cookie geldig is. Bijvoorbeeld: als u <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> invoert, is de cookie ook geldig voor subdomeinen zoals <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / Settings / HintNumber of days until the visitor is asked again for their consent. Remember to adjust the <translation-key id="Cookie-Lifetime">Cookie Lifetime</translation-key> information of the <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> under <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Aantal dagen tot de bezoeker opnieuw om toestemming wordt gevraagd. Pas ook de informatie aan van <translation-key id="Cookie-Lifetime">Cookie levenslang</translation-key> van de <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> onder <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintThe path for which the cookie is valid. Default path: <strong>{{ networkPath }}</strong>'=>'Het pad waarvoor de cookie geldig is. Standaardpad: <strong>{{ networkPath }}</strong>','Backend / Settings / HintThe <translation-key id="SameSite-Attribute">SameSite attribute</translation-key> defines how the browser should handle cookies in cross-site requests. We recommend using the <strong>Lax</strong> option.'=>'Het <translation-key id="SameSite-Attribute">SameSite-attribuut</translation-key> definieert hoe de browser moet omgaan met cookies bij cross-site verzoeken. We raden u aan om de optie <strong>lax</strong> te gebruiken.','Backend / Settings / HintA cookie with the <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure attribute</translation-key> is sent to the server only in case of an encrypted request via the HTTPS protocol.'=>'Een cookie met het <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure-attribuut</translation-key> wordt uitsluitend bij een versleuteld verzoek via het HTTPS-protocol verzonden naar de server.','Backend / Settings / HintShows the version of the cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Increases with activating <translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Update Cookie Version &amp; Force Re-Selection</translation-key>.'=>'Toont de versie van de cookie van <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Dit verhoogt zodra <translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Versie van cookie bijwerken &amp; opnieuw selecteren forceren</translation-key> wordt geactiveerd.','Backend / Settings / HintA bot/crawler is treated like a visitor who accepted all <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>.'=>'Een bot/crawler wordt behandeld als een bezoeker die alle <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> heeft geaccepteerd.','Backend / Settings / HintAdd one URL per line. Insert WordPress Address (URL). URL must end with <strong>/</strong>. Consent will be shared between websites.'=>'Voeg één URL per regel toe. Voeg een WordPress-adres (URL) in. De URL moet eindigen op <strong>/</strong>. De toestemmingen worden tussen de websites gedeeld.','Backend / Settings / HintDisplay the <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> on the selected post types. The <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> allows you to add custom JavaScript on specific pages.'=>'Toon de <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Metabox</translation-key> op de geselecteerde berichttypes. Met de <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Metabox</translation-key> kunt u aangepaste JavaScripts toevoegen op specifieke pagina\'s.','Backend / Settings / HintIf enabled, the website will be reloaded after the visitor saves their consent.'=>'Als dit is ingeschakeld, wordt de website opnieuw geladen nadat de bezoeker de toestemming heeft opgeslagen.','Backend / Settings / HintIf enabled, the website will be reloaded after the visitor opt out.'=>'Als dit is ingeschakeld, wordt de website opnieuw geladen nadat de bezoeker zich heeft afgemeld.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Settings">Settings</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Bevestig dat u alle <translation-key id="Settings">Instellingen</translation-key> wilt resetten. Alle instellingen worden gereset naar de standaardinstellingen.','Backend / Settings / HintA visitor with active <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Do Not Track&quot;</translation-key> setting will not see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> automatically selects the <translation-key id="Accept-Only-Essential">Accept Only Essential</translation-key> option.'=>'Een bezoeker met de ingeschakelde instelling <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Niet tracken&quot;</translation-key> krijgt het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key> niet te zien en <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> selecteert automatisch de optie <translation-key id="Accept-Only-Essential">Alleen essentiële accepteren</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintWith Setup Mode enabled, you can test your setup without having to enable <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie Status</translation-key>. Only you will see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> on your website.'=>'Als de instellingenmodus is ingeschakeld, kunt u uw instelling testen zonder dat u de <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Status van Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> hoeft in te schakelen. Alleen u zult het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key> zien op uw website.','Backend / Settings / HintUpdates the version of the cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. This will cause the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> to reappear for visitors who have already selected an option.'=>'Werkt de versie van de cookie van <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> bij. Hierdoor wordt het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key> opnieuw getoond aan bezoekers die al een optie hebben geselecteerd.','Backend / Settings / TextVersion'=>'Versie','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextWhen you have to aggregate the consent:'=>'Wanneer u toestemmingen moet samenvoegen:','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if one site is using only the domain (e.g. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong>) and the other site a subdomain (e.g. <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)'=>'- als de ene site alleen het domein gebruikt (bijv. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong>) en de andere site een subdomein (bijv. <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if one site is using the root folder <strong>/</strong> and the other site a subfolder (e.g. <strong>/shop</strong>)'=>'- als de ene site de hoofdmap <strong>/</strong> gebruikt en de andere site een submap (bijv. <strong>/winkel</strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextWhen you can separate the consent:'=>'Wanneer u toestemmingen kunt scheiden:','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if all sites are using different domains (e.g. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> and <strong><em>my-example.com</em></strong>) or different subdomains (e.g. <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong> and <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)'=>'- als alle sites verschillende domeinen gebruiken (bijv. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> en <strong><em>my-example.com</em></strong>) of verschillende subdomeinen (bijv. <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong> en <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if all sites are using different subfolders (e.g. <strong>/en</strong> and <strong>/de</strong>)'=>'- als alle sites verschillende submappen gebruiken (bijv. <strong>/nl</strong> en <strong>/de</strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextThe visitor\'s consent is transferred to all specified domains and WordPress installations, provided the websites are set up in the same way (<translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> IDs must match). Any consent or modification by the visitor will be shared with the specified domains.'=>'De toestemming van de bezoeker wordt overgedragen naar alle opgegeven domeinen en WordPress-installaties, mits de websites op dezelfde manier zijn ingesteld (de ID\'s van <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> en <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key> moeten overeenkomen). Elke toestemming of aanpassing van de bezoeker wordt gedeeld met de opgegeven domeinen.','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>More information about <translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross Cookie Domains</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>'=>'<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>Meer informatie over <translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross-domein cookie - Domeinen</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>','Backend / Settings / Things to know / HeadlineAggregate Consents'=>'Toestemmingen samenvoegen','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross Cookie Domains</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross-domein cookie - Domeinen</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the Cookie Version?'=>'Wat is de versie van de cookie?','Backend / Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the Meta Box?'=>'Wat is de metabox?','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextThe cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> is assigned a version number. It is used to ask the visitor again for their consent if changes have been made to the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>. If the version number in the cookie differs from the current version number, the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> appears to the visitor.'=>'De cookie van <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> krijgt een versienummer toegewezen. Dit nummer wordt gebruikt om de bezoeker opnieuw om toestemming te vragen als er wijzigingen zijn aangebracht in de <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>. Als het versienummer in de cookie afwijkt van het huidige versienummer, wordt het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key> getoond aan de bezoeker.','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextIf active the <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> is displayed in the selected post types. This allows you to execute code (JavaScript, HTML, <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key>) on the page and e.g. trigger a conversion pixel.'=>'Als dit is ingeschakeld, wordt de <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Metabox</translation-key> getoond in de geselecteerde typen berichten. Hiermee kunt u code (JavaScript, HTML, <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key>) uitvoeren op de pagina en bijvoorbeeld een conversiepixel activeren.','Backend / Settings / URLhttps://borlabs.io/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&amp;utm_medium=Footer+Logo&amp;utm_campaign=Analysis'=>'https://borlabs.io/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&amp;utm_medium=Footer+Logo&amp;utm_campaign=Analysis','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Bewerken: {{ name }}','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbStyle Blockers'=>'Style blockers','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nieuw','Backend / Script Blocker / Field LabelContent Blocker Global JavaScript'=>'Content blocker voor JavaScript Wereldwijd','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelHandles'=>'Handles','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelName'=>'Naam','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelPhrases'=>'Zinnen','Backend / Script Blocker / LabelService Opt-in Script Tag'=>'Opt-in scripttag van service','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Configuration'=>'Configuratie van style blocker','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Information'=>'Informatie over style blocker','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Settings'=>'Style blocker-instellingen','Backend / Script Blocker / HintIf your intention is to unblock previously blocked <translation-key id="Styles">Styles</translation-key> upon unblocking a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, please insert the provided JavaScript into the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field within your <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> settings.'=>'Als u eerder geblokkeerde <translation-key id="Styles">Stijlen</translation-key> wilt deblokkeren nadat u een <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> hebt gedeblokkeerd, voegt u het meegeleverde JavaScript in het veld <translation-key id="Global">Wereldwijd</translation-key> in de instellingen van uw <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blocker / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> moet worden ingesteld. De <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> moet minstens 3 tekens lang zijn en mag alleen het volgende bevatten: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Style Blocker / HintThe name of the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'De naam van de <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blocker / HintTo allow the unblocking of previously blocked <translation-key id="Styles">Styles</translation-key> through user consent for a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, please insert the ensuing script tag into the field labeled <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> within your <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Om het deblokkeren van eerder geblokkeerde <translation-key id="Styles">Stijlen</translation-key> door middel van toestemming van de gebruiker voor een <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> mogelijk te maken, voegt u de volgende scripttag in het veld met de label <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt-in</translation-key> in van uw <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blocker / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>. If the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is disabled, it will not block stylesheets and style-tags.'=>'De status van deze <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>. Als de <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> is uitgeschakeld, worden stylesheets en stijltags niet geblokkeerd.','Backend / Style Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'U heeft geen <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> geconfigureerd.','Backend / Style Blockers / BreadcrumbStyle Blockers'=>'Style blockers','Backend / Style Blockers / HeadlineStyle Blockers'=>'Style blockers','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineHandles'=>'Handles','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Naam','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlinePhrases'=>'Zinnen','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> section?'=>'Wat is het doel van de sectie <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blockers</translation-key>?','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Uitleg over symbolen','Backend / Style Blockers / Tip / HeadlineLanguage independent'=>'Taalonafhankelijk','Backend / Style Blockers / Tip / Text<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> are configured independently for all languages.'=>'<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blockers</translation-key> worden afzonderlijk geconfigureerd voor alle talen.','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> section allows you to block <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> from <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> that, for example, embed <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> to load external fonts like <translation-key id="Google-Fonts">Google Fonts</translation-key>.'=>'Met de sectie <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blockers</translation-key> kunt u <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> blokkeren van <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> die bijvoorbeeld <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> insluiten om externe lettertypen zoals <translation-key id="Google-Fonts">Google Fonts</translation-key> te laden.','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / TextOnce a <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is created, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> provides an unblock JavaScript that can be entered into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. The <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> becomes unblocked once a visitor consents to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Zodra een <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> is aan gemaakt, biedt <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> een JavaScript voor het deblokkeren, dat kan worden ingevoerd in het veld <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt-in</translation-key> van een <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. De <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> wordt gedeblokkeerd zodra een bezoeker toestemming geeft voor de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is enabled and actively prevents <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> execution if the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key> matches a term configured in the system.'=>'De <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> is ingeschakeld en voorkomt actief dat <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> wordt uitgevoerd als de <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Phrases">Zinnen</translation-key> overeenkomen met een term die in het systeem is geconfigureerd.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for a <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'Verwijder de <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>. Niet beschikbaar voor een <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> die via de <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Bibliotheek</translation-key> is geïnstalleerd.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Bewerk de <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is inactive, allowing all <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> are executed without filtering or restricting based on <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>.'=>'De <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> is inactief. Hierdoor worden alle <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> uitgevoerd, zonder daarbij te filteren of te beperken op basis van <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Phrases">Zinnen</translation-key>.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageConnecting to the API failed. Please check that Wordpress has access to the Internet or retry later.'=>'Het verbinden met de API is mislukt. Controleer de internetverbinding van Wordpress of probeer het later opnieuw.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageMoving the database file failed.'=>'Het verplaatsen van het databasebestand is mislukt.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessagePlease enable GeoIP before downloading the database.'=>'Voordat u de database downloadt, moet u GeoIP inschakelen.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageThe database was successfully updated.'=>'De database is met succes bijgewerkt.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageYou already have the most up-to-date database.'=>'U beschikt al over de nieuwste database.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageUnpacking the database to the temporary folder failed. Please check if the temporary folder is writable and the PHP module ZIP is installed.'=>'Het uitpakken van de database naar de tijdelijke map is mislukt. Controleer of de tijdelijke map overschrijfbaar is en of de PHP-module ZIP is geïnstalleerd.','Backend / Model Localization / ModelCompatibility Patch'=>'Compatibiliteitspatch','Backend / Model Localization / ModelContent Blocker'=>'Content blocker','Backend / Model Localization / ModelProvider'=>'Provider','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Tracking">Tracking</translation-key> cookies are used to analyze user behavior on the website and to optimize the website based on the results.'=>'<translation-key id="Tracking">Tracking</translation-key> cookies worden gebruikt om het gedrag van gebruikers op de website te analyseren en de website op basis van de resultaten te optimaliseren.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>: Choose where information is stored in the browser. <translation-key id="HTTP">HTTP</translation-key> cookies are commonly used, alternatives like <translation-key id="Local-Storage">Local Storage</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Session-Storage">Session Storage</translation-key> do not possess predetermined lifetimes.'=>'<translation-key id="Type">Type</trans