r'=>'Nooit','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineLifetime'=>'Levenslang','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineName'=>'Naam','Backend / Library / HintThe <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> are included in this package and are necessary for the proper functioning of this package. They are installed when you click the <translation-key id="Button-Install">Install</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstall</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Update</translation-key> button. You can locate them later using the displayed name and key in the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> view (<translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Services">Services</translation-key>).'=>'De <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> zijn opgenomen in dit pakket en zijn noodzakelijk voor de goede werking van dit pakket. U installeert ze door te klikken op <translation-key id="Button-Install">Installeren</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Opnieuw installeren</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Bijwerken</translation-key>. U kunt ze later terugvinden met behulp van de getoonde naam en sleutel in het scherm <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Toestemmingsbeheer</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Services">Services</translation-key>).','Backend / Services / Table HeadlinePurpose'=>'Doel','Backend / Library / HintThe <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> are included in this package and are necessary for the proper functioning of this package. They are installed when you click the <translation-key id="Button-Install">Install</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstall</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Update</translation-key> button. You can locate them later using the displayed name and key in the <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> view (<translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key>).'=>'De <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blockers</translation-key> zijn opgenomen in dit pakket en zijn noodzakelijk voor de goede werking van dit pakket. U installeert ze door te klikken op <translation-key id="Button-Install">Installeren</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Opnieuw installeren</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Bijwerken</translation-key>. U kunt ze later terugvinden met behulp van de getoonde naam en sleutel in het scherm <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blockers</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Style-Blockers">Style blockers</translation-key>).','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineType'=>'Type','Backend / Library / NavigationAll'=>'Alle','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextIf you enable this option <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> searches and deletes cookies that match the <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>). You can also use <strong>*</strong> to search for multiple names, e.g. if you enter the Name <strong><em>example_*</em></strong> <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> will search and delete the cookies <strong><em>example_abc</em></strong> and <strong><em>example_xyz</em></strong>.'=>'Als u deze optie inschakelt, zoekt en verwijdert <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> cookies die overeenkomen met de <translation-key id="Name">Naam</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Name">Naam</translation-key>). U kunt ook <strong>*</strong> gebruiken om te zoeken naar meerdere namen. Als u bijvoorbeeld de Naam <strong><em>example_*</em></strong> invoert, zal <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> de cookies <strong><em>example_abc</em></strong> en <strong><em>example_xyz</em></strong> zoeken en verwijderen.','Backend / Library / NavigationFilter'=>'Filteren','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThis function is mainly intended to delete session cookies set by third-party plugins via PHP. JavaScript cookies can also be deleted, but only if they belong to the same domain and do not have the <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure attribute</translation-key>.'=>'Deze functie is voornamelijk bedoeld om sessiecookies te verwijderen die door plug-ins van derden zijn ingesteld via PHP. JavaScript-cookies kunnen ook worden verwijderd, maar alleen als ze tot hetzelfde domein behoren en niet het <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure-attribuut</translation-key> hebben.','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Compatibility Patches</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Compatibiliteitspatches</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextExample: if the website operates under <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>, no cookie associated with <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> can be deleted.'=>'Bijvoorbeeld: als de website actief is onder <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>, worden de cookies verwijderd die niet gekoppeld zijn aan <strong><em>example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content blockers</t