-key>.','Backend / Library / TextPackage'=>'Pakket','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextIn the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> section (found under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Providers</translation-key>), you will find more information and also have the option to edit or create new <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> entries.'=>'In de sectie <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> (onder <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Toestemmingsbeheer</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Providers</translation-key>) vindt u meer informatie en hebt u ook de mogelijkheid om invoeren van een nieuwe <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> aan te maken of te bewerken.','Backend / Library / TextRecommended'=>'Aanbevolen','Backend / License / Alert MessagePlease activate your license key first. <a href="?page=borlabs-cookie-license">Click here</a> to enter your license key.'=>'Activeer eerst uw licentiesleutel. <a href="?page=borlabs-cookie-license">Klik hier</a> om uw licentiesleutel in te voeren.','Backend / License / Alert MessagePlease enter your license key to receive updates.'=>'Voer uw licentiesleutel in om updates te ontvangen.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> can be used to execute custom code associated with this type of <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> once the visitor has given consent to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. This can be used, for example, to block a conversion pixel code.'=>'De <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> kan worden gebruikt om aangepaste code uit te voeren die is gekoppeld aan dit type <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, zodra de bezoeker toestemming heeft gegeven voor de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Dit kan bijvoorbeeld worden gebruikt om een pixelcode voor conversie te blokkeren.','Backend / License / Alert MessageYour license key is not valid.'=>'Uw licentiesleutel is niet geldig.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> for example can be used in the <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. You can find it for example in <translation-key id="Posts">Posts</translation-key> &raquo; <em><translation-key id="Your-Post">Your Post</translation-key></em> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Custom-Code">Custom Code</translation-key>.'=>'De <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> kan bijvoorbeeld worden gebruikt in de <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Metabox</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. U kunt het bijvoorbeeld vinden via <translation-key id="Posts">Berichten</translation-key> &raquo; <em><translation-key id="Your-Post">Uw bericht</translation-key></em> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Custom-Code">Aangepaste code</translation-key>.','Backend / License / Alert MessageYour license request is not valid.'=>'Uw licentieaanvraag is niet geldig.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> are not available until the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is created.'=>'De <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> zijn beschikbaar zodra de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is aangemaakt.','Backend / Services / LabelAsynchronous Opt-out Code'=>'Asynchrone code opt-out','Backend / Services / LabelBlock Cookies Before Consent'=>'Cookies blokkeren voor toestemming','Backend / Services / Label<translation-key id="Prioritize">Prioritize</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Prioritize">Prioriteit geven</translation-key>','Backend / Services / HintThe <translation-key id="Opt-out-Code">Opt-out Code</translation-key> contains asynchronous JavaScript code that needs to executed to finish the Opt-out.'=>'De <translation-key id="Opt-out-Code">Code opt-out</translation-key> bevat asynchrone JavaScript-code die moet worden uitgevoerd om de opt-out te voltooien.','Backend / Services / HintIf enabled, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> tries to block cookies with the names from <translation-key id="Cookie-Name">Cookie Name</translation-key> until consent is given.'=>'Als dit is ingeschakeld (Status: AAN), probeert <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> de cookies met de namen uit <translation-key id="Cookie-Name">Cookienaam</translation-key> te blokkeren totdat hiervoor toestemming is gegeven.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense information refreshed successfully.'=>'Licentie-informatie succesvol ververst.','Backend / Services / HintThe <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> is loaded in <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> and is executed before the page is fully loaded.'=>'De <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt-in</translation-key> is geladen in <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> en wordt uitgevoerd voordat de pagina volledig is geladen.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense registered successfully.'=>'Licentie succesvol geregistreerd.','Backend / Service Location / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Location">Location</translation-key> configured.'=>'Er is geen <translation-key id="Location">Adres</translation-key> geconfigureerd.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense removed successfully.'=>'Licentie succesvol verwijderd.','Backend / Service Location / ButtonAdd Location'=>'Adres toevoegen','Backend / Service Location / LabelHostname'=>'Hostnaam','Backend / License / BreadcrumbLicense'=>'Licentie','Backend / Service Location / LabelPath'=>'Pad','Backend / License / Button TitleRefresh License Information'=>'Licentie-informatie vernieuwen','Backend / Service Location / Headline<translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Locations">Adressen</translation-key>','Backend / License / Button TitleRemove License'=>'Licentie verwijderen','Backend / Service Location / Table HeadlineHostname'=>'Hostnaam','Backend / License / LabelCloud Scans'=>'Cloud scans','Backend / Service Location / Table HeadlinePath'=>'Pad','Backend / License / LabelConfirm Refresh'=>'Vernieuwen bevestigen','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is a <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>?'=>'Wat is een <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostnaam</translation-key>?','Backend / License / LabelLicense Key'=>'Licentiesleutel','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key> section?'=>'Wat is het doel van de sectie <translation-key id="Locations">Adressen</translation-key>?','Backend / License / LabelLicense Name'=>'Licentienaam','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is the domain name of the website. For example, if the URL of the website is <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, the <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'De <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostnaam</translation-key> is de domeinnaam van de website. Als de URL van de website bijvoorbeeld <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong> is, dan is de <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostnaam</translation-key> <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / License / LabelLicense Status'=>'Licentiestatus','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / TextIt may happen that an embedded <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> on your website does not set a cookie, but a connection to a foreign domain is established. Therefore, it is advisable to record this domain here and thus name the service responsible for it, so that interested visitors can understand why this external connection occurs.'=>'Het kan zo zijn dat een ingesloten <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> op uw website geen cookie instelt, maar dat er een verbinding met een buitenlands domein tot stand wordt gebracht. Daarom is het raadzaam om dit domein hier te registreren en de naam op te geven van de service die hiervoor verantwoordelijk is, zodat geïnteresseerde bezoekers weten waarom deze externe verbinding tot stand komt.','Backend / License / LabelValid Until'=>'Geldig tot','Backend / Service Option / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Option">Option</translation-key> configured.'=>'Er is geen <translation-key id="Option">Optie</translation-key> geconfigureerd.','Backend / License / LabelMax Websites'=>'Maximaal aantal websites','Backend / Service Option / ButtonAdd Option'=>'Optie toevoegen','Backend / License / LabelRefresh'=>'Vernieuwen','Backend / Service Option / LabelDescription'=>'Beschrijving','Backend / License / Headline<translation-key id="Remove-License">Remove License</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Remove-License">Licentie verwijderen</translation-key>','Backend / Service Option / Headline<translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Options">Opties</translation-key>','Backend / License / HeadlineYour License'=>'Uw licentie','Backend / Service Option / Table HeadlineDescription'=>'Beschrijving','Backend / License / HeadlineYour License Information'=>'Informatie over uw licentie','Backend / Service Option / Table Headline<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>','Backend / License / HintEnter your License Key.'=>'Voer uw licentiesleutel in.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> section?'=>'Wat is het doel van de sectie <translation-key id="Options">Opties</translation-key>?','Backend / License / HintPlease confirm that you want to remove your license data from this website. After the license data is removed you are able to enter your new license key.'=>'Bevestig dat u uw licentiegegevens van deze website wilt verwijderen. Nadat de licentiegegevens zijn verwijderd, kunt u uw nieuwe licentiesleutel invoeren.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / TextWith <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> you can provide more information about the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. There are six <translation-key id="Types">Types</translation-key> to choose from and you can add as many <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> as you like.'=>'Met <translation-key id="Options">Opties</translation-key> kunt u meer informatie geven over de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. U kunt kiezen uit zes <translation-key id="Types">Typen</translation-key> en u kunt zoveel <translation-key id="Options">Opties</translation-key> toevoegen als u maar wilt.','Backend / License / TextYour license has expired.'=>'Uw licentie is verlopen.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / TextFor example, you could select the &quot;<translation-key id="Location-Processing">Location Processing</translation-key>&quot; <translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key> and add <strong>United States of America</strong> as description if the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> processes data in the United States.'=>'U kunt bijvoorbeeld kiezen voor &quot;<translation-key id="Location-Processing">Verwerkingslocatie</translation-key>&quot; <translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key> en de <strong>Verenigde Staten</strong> toevoegen als beschrijving als de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> gegevens verwerkt in de Verenigde Staten.','Backend / License / TextYour license is valid.'=>'Uw licentie is geldig.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> configured.'=>'Er is geen <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> geconfigureerd.','Backend / License / Things to know / HeadlineTransferring a license key to a new website'=>'Een licentiesleutel overzetten naar een nieuwe website','Backend / License / Things to know / TextYou can use the <translation-key id="Remove-License">Remove License</translation-key> option to remove the license from this website, or you can visit our <translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Customer Portal</translation-key> and remove the license from there.'=>'U kunt de optie <translation-key id="Remove-License">Licentie verwijderen</translation-key> gebruiken om de licentie van deze website te verwijderen of u kunt onze <translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Klantenportaal</translation-key> bezoeken en de licentie daar verwijderen.','Backend / License / Things to know / Text<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span><translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Customer Portal</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>'=>'<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span><translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Klantenportaal</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>','Backend / Local Scanner / TextAn error has occurred. Please check your browser\'s console for an error message. If the issue persists even after trying again and switching to <translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scan Mode</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Manual">Manual</translation-key>, kindly reach out to our support team for assistance.'=>'Er is een fout opgetreden. Controleer de console van uw browser voor een foutmelding. Als het probleem zich blijft voordoen, zelfs nadat u het opnieuw hebt geprobeerd en bent overgeschakeld op <translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scanmodus</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Manual">Handmatig</translation-key>, neem dan contact op met ons supportteam voor hulp.','Backend / Services / HeadlineReset Default Services'=>'Standaardservices resetten','Backend / Local Scanner / ButtonRun scan'=>'Scan uitvoeren','Backend / Services / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> and the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> are not reset.'=>'Bevestig dat u alle instellingen van de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> wilt resetten. Ze worden gereset naar de standaardinstellingen. Uw aangepaste <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> en de <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> die via de <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Bibliotheek</translation-key> zijn geïnstalleerd, worden niet gereset.','Backend / Local Scanner / LabelPage to scan'=>'Pagina scannen','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Local Scanner / Label<translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scan Mode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scanmodus</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Table HeadlinePosition'=>'Positie','Backend / Local Scanner / Label<translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Zoekzin</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineScan Progress'=>'Vooruitgang van scan','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> section?'=>'Wat is het doel van de sectie <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>?','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineScan Settings'=>'Scaninstellingen','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Uitleg over symbolen','Backend / Local Scanner / HintThe string <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> is looking for. Separate multiple entries with a comma.'=>'De tekenreeks waar <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> naar op zoek is. Scheid meerdere invoeren met een komma.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextIn the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> section you can document the use of services and their cookies for your visitors, as well as integrate JavaScripts, such as Google Analytics.'=>'In de sectie <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> kunt u het gebruik van services en hun cookies voor uw bezoekers documenteren en JavaScripts integreren, zoals Google Analytics.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextBecause <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> uses the opt-in process, JavaScripts are only executed after the visitor has given their consent to the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Omdat <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> het opt-in-proces gebruikt, worden JavaScripts pas uitgevoerd nadat de bezoeker toestemming heeft gegeven voor de <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Scan-Modes">Scan Modes</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Scan-Modes">Scanmodi</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is active and displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'De <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is actief en wordt getoond in het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key>. Niet beschikbaar voor de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Current-User">Current User</translation-key>:<br>The scan is performed as the currently logged in user. This may affect the results if the user has different rights than a guest user.'=>'<translation-key id="Current-User">Huidige gebruiker</translation-key>:<br>de scan wordt uitgevoerd in naam van de gebruiker die momenteel is aangemeld. Dit kan de resultaten beïnvloeden als de gebruiker andere rechten heeft dan een gastgebruiker.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Verwijder de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Niet beschikbaar voor de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineFor example: Some plugins do not embed tracking JavaScript for users with the role of an administrator.'=>'Bijvoorbeeld: sommige plugins sluiten geen tracking JavaScript in voor gebruikers met de rol van administrator.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Bewerk de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Guest">Guest</translation-key>:<br>The scan is performed as a guest user. This is the default setting.'=>'<translation-key id="Guest">Gast</translation-key>:<br>de scan wordt uitgevoerd als gastgebruiker. Dit is de standaardinstelling.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is inactive and not displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'De <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is inactief en wordt niet getoond in het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key>. Niet beschikbaar voor de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Manual">Manual</translation-key>:<br>When you use this mode, a signed URL is provided that you can use to run the scan by clicking on it. This is useful if the scan cannot be performed due to a server configuration or if your website is not accessible from the outside (<translation-key id="Local-Environment">Local Environment</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Staging-Environment">Staging Environment</translation-key>), for example.'=>'<translation-key id="Manual">Handmatig</translation-key>:<br>als u deze modus gebruikt, wordt een ondertekende URL geleverd om de scan uit te voeren door erop te klikken. Dit is bijvoorbeeld handig als de scan niet kan worden uitgevoerd vanwege een serverconfiguratie of als uw website niet toegankelijk is van buitenaf (zoals een <translation-key id="Local-Environment">Lokale omgeving</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Staging-Environment">Staging-omgeving</translation-key>).','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Bewerken: {{ name }}','Backend / Local Scanner / Alert MessageNo scan result available.'=>'Er is geen scanresultaat beschikbaar.','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbService Groups'=>'Servicegroepen','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Matched Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Overeenkomende handles</translation-key>','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nieuw','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Matched Tags</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Overeenkomende tags</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelDescription'=>'Beschrijving','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Unmatched Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Niet overeenkomende handles</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Unmatched Tags</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Niet overeenkomende tags</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelName'=>'Naam','Backend / Local Scanner / HintSpecifies the name of the object that must be present for the script from the <strong>Tag</strong> column to be executed. Allowed characters include $, _, letters (both upper and lower case), and numbers. The first character must be $, _, or a letter, while subsequent characters can also include numbers.'=>'Specificeert de naam van het object dat aanwezig moet zijn om het script uit de kolom <strong>tag</strong> uit te voeren. Toegestane tekens zijn $, _, letters (zowel hoofdletters als kleine letters) en cijfers. Het eerste teken moet $, _ of een letter zijn en de volgende tekens kunnen ook getallen zijn.','Backend / Service Groups / LabelPosition'=>'Positie','Backend / Local Scanner / HintEnter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the script. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other JavaScripts as well.'=>'Voer een unieke tekenreeks in uit de <strong>tag</strong> om het script te blokkeren. Deze moet uniek zijn en mag niet aanwezig zijn in andere JavaScripts.','Backend / Service Groups / LabelPre-selected'=>'Voorgeselecteerd','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineBlock'=>'Blokkeren','Backend / Service Groups / Label<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineService Group Information'=>'Informatie over servicegroep','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Zin</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineService Group Settings'=>'Servicegroep-instellingen','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineTag'=>'Tag','Backend / Service Groups / HintEnter a description for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. It is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Voer een beschrijving in voor deze <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key>. Deze wordt aan de bezoeker getoond in het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineType'=>'Type','Backend / Service Groups / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> moet worden ingesteld. De <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> moet minstens 3 tekens lang zijn en mag alleen het volgende bevatten: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineURL'=>'URL','Backend / Service Groups / HintChoose a name for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. It is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Kies een naam voor deze <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key>. Deze wordt aan de bezoeker getoond in het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> are used to identify the JavaScript files that are loaded on your website. For example, your installed <translation-key id="Themes">Themes</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> use the WordPress function <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_script/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_script()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to define the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> worden gebruikt om de JavaScript-bestanden te identificeren die op uw website worden geladen. Zo gebruiken uw geïnstalleerde <translation-key id="Themes">Thema\'s</translation-key> en <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> de WordPress-functie <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_script/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_script()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> om de <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> te definiëren.','Backend / Service Groups / HintDetermine the position where this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is displayed. Order follows natural numbers.'=>'Bepaal de positie waar deze <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key> wordt weergegeven. De volgorde wordt bepaald op basis van natuurlijke getallen.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> are used to identify the <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> files that are loaded on your website. For example, your installed <translation-key id="Themes">Themes</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> use the WordPress function <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_style/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_style()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to define the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> worden gebruikt om de <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>-bestanden te identificeren die op uw website worden geladen. Zo gebruiken uw geïnstalleerde <translation-key id="Themes">Thema\'s</translation-key> en <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> de WordPress-functie <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_style/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_style()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> om de <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> te definiëren.','Backend / Service Groups / HintIf enabled, this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is pre-selected in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. The visitor can de-select it.'=>'Als dit is ingeschakeld (Status: AAN), wordt deze <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key> vooraf geselecteerd in het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key>. De bezoeker kan de selectie ongedaan maken.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Matched Handles</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> that matches your <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Overeenkomende handles</translation-key>:<br>dit zijn <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> die overeenkomen met uw <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Zoekzin</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / HintUse this <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to unblock JavaScript or content when user opted-in for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>.'=>'Gebruik deze <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> om JavaScript of inhoud te deblokkeren wanneer de gebruiker zich heeft aangemeld voor deze <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Unmatched Handles</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> that do not match a <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key> but were found during the scan and maybe relevant.'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Niet overeenkomende handles</translation-key>:<br>dit zijn <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> die niet overeenkomen met een <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Zoekzin</translation-key>, maar zijn gevonden tijdens het scannen en relevant kunnen zijn.','Backend / Service Groups / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. If enabled it is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'De status van deze <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key>. Als dit is ingeschakeld (Status: AAN), wordt deze aan de bezoeker getoond in het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> explained'=>'Uitleg over <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> ','Backend / Service Groups / Input Placeholder...block this...'=>'...blokkeer dit...','Backend / Local Scanner / Things to know / HeadlineInput fields explained'=>'Uitleg over invoervelden','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> explained'=>'Uitleg over <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> ','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> explained'=>'Uitleg over <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> can be used to execute custom code once the visitor has given consent to a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> associated with this type of <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. This can be used, for example, to block a conversion pixel code.'=>'De <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> kan worden gebruikt om aangepaste code uit te voeren zodra de bezoeker toestemming heeft gegeven voor een <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> die is verbonden aan dit type <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegroep</translation-key>. U kunt dit bijvoorbeeld gebruiken voor het blokkeren van een pixelcode voor een conversie.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> refer to <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong> tags that lack an associated <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, which can occur when JavaScript is embedded directly into your website\'s HTML code, bypassing the dedicated WordPress function typically used for this purpose'=>'<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> verwijzen naar <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong>-tags zonder gekoppelde <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, wat kan optreden als JavaScript direct in de HTML-code van uw website wordt ingesloten, waarbij de hiervoor gebruikelijke WordPress-functie wordt omzeild','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> refer to <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> tags and <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong> tags that lack an associated <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, which can occur when <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> is embedded directly into your website\'s HTML code, bypassing the dedicated WordPress function typically used for this purpose'=>'<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> verwijzen naar <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong>-tags en <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong>-tags zonder gekoppelde <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, wat kan optreden als <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> direct in de HTML-code van uw website wordt ingesloten, waarbij de hiervoor gebruikelijke WordPress-functie wordt omzeild','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Matched Tags</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> that matches your <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Overeenkomende tags</translation-key>:<br>dit zijn <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> die overeenkomen met uw <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Zoekzin</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Unmatched Tags</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> that do not match a <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key> but were found during the scan and maybe relevant.'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Niet overeenkomende tags</translation-key>:<br>dit zijn <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> die niet overeenkomen met een <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Zoekzin</translation-key>, maar zijn gevonden tijdens het scannen en relevant kunnen zijn.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>:<br>Enter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the script. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other JavaScripts as well.'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Zin</translation-key>:<br>voer een unieke tekenreeks in uit de <strong>Tag</strong> om het script te blokkeren. Deze moet uniek zijn en mag niet aanwezig zijn in andere JavaScripts.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>:<br>This feature is optional and ensures that once the JavaScript is unblocked, it does not execute until the object specified in the <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> column is present on the website. This capability facilitates the resolution of race condition issues.'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>:<br>deze functie is optioneel en zorgt ervoor dat zodra het JavaScript is gedeblokkeerd. Het wordt niet uitgevoerd totdat het object dat is opgegeven in de kolom <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> aanwezig is op de website. Deze functie vergemakkelijkt het oplossen van problemen met race conditions.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineSpecifies the name of the object that must be present for the script from the <strong>Tag</strong> column to be executed. Allowed characters include $, _, letters (both upper and lower case), and numbers. The first character must be $, _, or a letter, while subsequent characters can also include numbers.'=>'Specificeert de naam van het object dat aanwezig moet zijn om het script uit de kolom <strong>tag</strong> uit te voeren. Toegestane tekens zijn $, _, letters (zowel hoofdletters als kleine letters) en cijfers. Het eerste teken moet $, _ of een letter zijn, terwijl de volgende tekens ook getallen kunnen zijn.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineExample:'=>'Bijvoorbeeld:','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineThe example initiates loading an external library and concurrently calls the <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> function. This could induce a race condition issue since, when <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> is invoked, the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> library—responsible for providing this method—might not yet be fully loaded.'=>'Het voorbeeld initieert het laden van een externe bibliotheek en roept tegelijkertijd de <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> functie aan. Dit kan een probleem met een race condition veroorzaken, omdat wanneer <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> wordt aangeroepen, de bibliotheek <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong>, die verantwoordelijk is voor deze methode, mogelijk nog niet volledig geladen is.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineTo mitigate this race condition, block both the script tag that loads the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> library and the script tag that calls <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>. For the script tag where <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> is called, enter <strong><em>calendarLibrary</em></strong> in the <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> field.'=>'Om deze ras condition te beperken, blokkeert u zowel de scripttag die de <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong>-bibliotheek en de scripttag die <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init() aanroept</em></strong>. Voor de scripttag waar <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> wordt aangeroepen, voert u <strong><em>calendarLibrary</em></strong> in het veld <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineIf the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is now unblocked, the script-tag containing <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> will not execute until the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> has completely loaded.'=>'Als de <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> nu is gedeblokkeerd, zal de scripttag met daarin <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> niet uitgevoerd totdat de <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> volledig geladen is.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>:<br>Enter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> tags or <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong> tags as well.'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Zin</translation-key>:<br>Voer een unieke tekenreeks in uit de <strong>Tag</strong> om de <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> te blokkeren. Deze moet uniek zijn en mag niet aanwezig zijn in andere <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong>-tags of <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong>-tags.','Backend / Local Scanner / ValidationThe phrase is not found in the JavaScript code on the left side.'=>'De zin is niet gevonden in de JavaScript-code aan de linkerkant.','Backend / Local Scanner / ValidationThe phrase is not unique and overlaps with a phrase for another JavaScript.'=>'De zin is niet uniek en komt al voor in een ander JavaScript.','Backend / Log / Alert MessageThe <translation-key id="Log">Log</translation-key> could not be found.'=>'Het <translation-key id="Log">Logboek</translation-key> kon niet worden gevonden.','Backend / Log / Breadcrumb<translation-key id="Logs">Logs</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Logs">Logboeken</translation-key>','Backend / Log / BreadcrumbDetails'=>'Details','Backend / Log / HeadlineProcess History'=>'Procesgeschiedenis','Backend / Log / FieldBacktrace'=>'Backtrace','Backend / Log / FieldContext'=>'Context','Backend / Log / FieldLevel'=>'Niveau','Backend / Log / FieldMessage'=>'Bericht','Backend / Log / FieldProcess ID'=>'Proces-ID','Backend / Log / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Logs">Logs</translation-key> found.'=>'Geen <translation-key id="Logs">Logboeken</translation-key> gevonden.','Backend / Log / Headline<translation-key id="Logs">Logs</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Logs">Logboeken</translation-key>','Backend / Log / PlaceholderSearch Process ID, Level or Message'=>'Zoek naar proces-ID, niveau of bericht','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineHas backtrace'=>'Heeft backtrace','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineHas context'=>'Heeft context','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineCreated at'=>'Aangemaakt op','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineLevel'=>'Niveau','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineMessage'=>'Bericht','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineProcess ID'=>'Proces-ID','Backend / MetaBox / Field<translation-key id="Custom-Code">Custom Code</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Custom-Code">Aangepaste code</translation-key>','Backend / MetaBox / HeadlineBorlabs Cookie - Meta Box'=>'Borlabs Cookie - Metabox','Backend / MetaBox / HintThe code you enter here will only run on this page. Extend your code by wrapping it with our blocking <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> to ensure that it only executes after you\'ve received consent. This functionality proves useful in scenarios such as needing to trigger a conversion pixel exclusively on this page.'=>'De code die u hier invoert, wordt alleen op deze pagina uitgevoerd. Breid uw code uit door deze te blokkeren met onze <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> zodat deze alleen wordt uitgevoerd nadat u toestemming hebt ontvangen. Deze functionaliteit is bijvoorbeeld handig als u alleen op deze pagina een pixel voor conversie wilt activeren.','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Bewerken: {{ name }}','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbProviders'=>'Providers','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nieuw','Backend / Providers / LabelAddress'=>'Adres','Backend / Providers / LabelCookie URL'=>'Cookie-URL','Backend / Providers / LabelDescription'=>'Beschrijving','Backend / Providers / Label<translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">IAB Vendor ID</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">IAB-Verkoper-ID</translation-key>','Backend / Providers / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Providers / LabelName'=>'Naam','Backend / Providers / LabelOpt-out URL'=>'URL opt-out','Backend / Providers / LabelPartners'=>'Partners','Backend / Providers / Label<translation-key id="Privacy-Url">Privacy URL</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Privacy-Url">Privacy-URL</translation-key>','Backend / Providers / HeadlineProvider Information'=>'Informatie over provider','Backend / Providers / LabelYou can optionally provide the <translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">IAB Vendor ID</translation-key> to add information about an IAB Vendor that is not part of the IAB TCF standard.'=>'U kunt ook de <translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">IAB-Verkoper-ID</translation-key> opgeven om informatie toe te voegen over een IAB-verkoper die geen deel uitmaakt van de IAB TCF-standaard.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> section?'=>'Wat is het doel van de sectie <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key>?','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextFor legal compliance, every <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> must be linked to a specific <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'Voor wettelijke naleving moet elke <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> worden gekoppeld aan een specifieke <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is the company that delivers the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> (e.g., Google Analytics) or the content (e.g., YouTube videos).'=>'De <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is het bedrijf dat de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> levert (bijv. Google Analytics) of de inhoud (bijv. YouTube-video\'s) levert.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextVisitors should receive clear information about the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> responsible for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> or blocked content.'=>'Bezoekers moeten duidelijke informatie ontvangen over de <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> die verantwoordelijk is voor de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> of de geblokkeerde inhoud.','Backend / Providers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> configured.'=>'Er is geen <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> geconfigureerd.','Backend / Providers / HeadlineProviders'=>'Providers','Backend / Providers / HeadlineReset Default Providers'=>'Standaardproviders resetten','Backend / Providers / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key>. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> and the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> are not reset.'=>'Bevestig dat u de <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> wilt resetten. Ze worden gereset naar hun standaardinstellingen. Uw aangepaste <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> en de <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> die via de <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Bibliotheek</translation-key> zijn geïnstalleerd, worden niet gereset.','Backend / Providers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Providers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Naam','Backend / Providers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Uitleg over symbolen','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Owner of this website</translation-key>.'=>'Verwijder de <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>. Niet beschikbaar voor de <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Eigenaar van deze website</translation-key>.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'Bewerk de <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Bewerken: {{ name }}','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbScript Blockers'=>'Script blockers','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nieuw','Backend / Script Blockers / Field LabelContent Blocker Global JavaScript'=>'Content blocker voor JavaScript Wereldwijd','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelHandles'=>'Handles','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelName'=>'Naam','Backend / Script Blockers / Label<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelPhrases'=>'Zinnen','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelService Opt-in Script Tag'=>'Opt-in scripttag van service','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Configuration'=>'Configuratie van style blocker','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Information'=>'Informatie over style blocker','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Settings'=>'Script blocker-instellingen','Backend / Script Blockers / HintIf your intention is to unblock previously blocked JavaScripts upon unblocking a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, please insert the provided JavaScript into the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field within your <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> settings.'=>'Als u eerder geblokkeerde JavaScripts wilt deblokkeren na het deblokkeren van een <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>, voegt u het meegeleverde JavaScript in het veld <translation-key id="Global">Wereldwijd</translation-key> in de instellingen van uw <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> moet worden ingesteld. De <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> moet minstens 3 tekens lang zijn en mag alleen het volgende bevatten: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Script Blockers / HintThe name of the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'De naam van de <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HintTo allow the unblocking of previously blocked JavaScripts through user consent for a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, please insert the ensuing script tag into the field labeled <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> within your <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Om het deblokkeren van eerder geblokkeerde JavaScripts met toestemming van de gebruiker voor een <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> mogelijk te maken, voegt u de volgende scripttag in het veld met de label <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt-in</translation-key> in uw <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> in.','Backend / Script Blockers / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>. If the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is disabled, it will not block JavaScript.'=>'De status van deze <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>. Als de <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> is uitgeschakeld, wordt JavaScript niet geblokkeerd.','Backend / Script Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'Er is geen <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> geconfigureerd.','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blockers'=>'Script blockers','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Naam','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="On-Exist">OnExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="On-Exist">OnExist</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Phrases">Zinnen</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> section?'=>'Wat is het doel van de sectie <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script blockers</translation-key>?','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Uitleg over symbolen','Backend / Script Blockers / Tip / HeadlineLanguage independent'=>'Taalonafhankelijk','Backend / Script Blockers / Tip / Text<translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> are configured independently for all languages.'=>'<translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script blockers</translation-key> worden afzonderlijk geconfigureerd voor alle talen.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> section allows you to block JavaScripts from <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> whose JavaScript you can\'t enter into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Met de sectie <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script blockers</translation-key> kunt u JavaScripts blokkeren van <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> waarvan u het JavaScript niet kunt invoeren in het veld <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt-in</translation-key> van een <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextOnce a <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is created, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> provides an unblock JavaScript that can be entered into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. The JavaScript becomes unblocked once a visitor consents to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Zodra een <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> is aangemaakt, geeft <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> een JavaScript om te kunnen deblokkeren. Deze code kan worden ingevoerd in het veld <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Code opt-in</translation-key> van een <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Het JavaScript wordt gedeblokkeerd zodra een bezoeker toestemming geeft voor de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextThis usually allows you to continue using your favorite plugins, but their JavaScript will only run when a visitor gave consent.'=>'Hierdoor kunt u meestal uw favoriete plugins blijven gebruiken, maar hun JavaScript wordt alleen uitgevoerd zodra een bezoeker hiervoor toestemming heeft gegeven.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is enabled and actively prevents JavaScript execution if the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key> matches a term configured in the system.'=>'De <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> is ingeschakeld en voorkomt actief dat JavaScript wordt uitgevoerd als de <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Phrases">Zinnen</translation-key> overeenkomen met een term die in het systeem is geconfigureerd.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for a <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'Verwijder de <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>. Niet beschikbaar voor een <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> die is geïnstalleerd via de <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Bibliotheek</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Bewerk de <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is inactive, allowing all JavaScript to execute without filtering or restricting based on <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>.'=>'De <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> is inactief, waardoor alle JavaScripts kunnen worden uitgevoerd zonder te filteren of te beperken op basis van <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Phrases">Zinnen</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Cookie / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> configured.'=>'Er is geen <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> geconfigureerd.','Backend / Service Cookie / ButtonAdd Cookie'=>'Cookie toevoegen','Backend / Service Cookie / FieldLifetime'=>'Levenslang','Backend / Service Cookie / FieldName'=>'Naam','Backend / Service Cookie / HeadlineCookies'=>'Cookies','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineDescription'=>'Beschrijving','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineHostname'=>'Hostnaam','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineLifetime'=>'Levenslang','Backend / Service Cookie / Table Headline<translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Name">Naam</translation-key>','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlinePath'=>'Pad','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlinePurpose'=>'Doel','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineType'=>'Type','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineYou may input all cookies utilized by the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> here. Typically, information regarding which cookies are used and their respective purposes can be found on the website of the service you intend to add. For instance, details about the cookies used by Google Analytics can be located in its knowledge base.'=>'U kunt hier alle cookies invoeren die door de <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> worden gebruikt. Over het algemeen is informatie over welke cookies worden gebruikt en hun respectievelijke doeleinden te vinden op de website van de service die u wilt toevoegen. Zo kunt u bijvoorbeeld details over de cookies die worden gebruikt door Google Analytics vinden in de kennisbank van Google.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section?'=>'Wat is het doel van de sectie <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key>?','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineInput fields explained'=>'Uitleg over invoervelden','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Description">Description</translation-key>: Enter a description of the cookie and explain its purpose. This is optional, but recommended.'=>'<translation-key id="Description">Beschrijving</translation-key>: voer een beschrijving van de cookie in en leg het doel uit. Dit is optioneel, maar aanbevolen.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineThe <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser\'s developer tools can be used to find the values for the <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key>, and <translation-key id="Lifetime">Lifetime</translation-key> fields.'=>'De sectie <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> van de ontwikkelaarstools van uw browser kan worden gebruikt om de waarden voor de velden <translation-key id="Name">Naam</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostnaam</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Path">Pad</translation-key> en <translation-key id="Lifetime">Levenslang</translation-key> te vinden.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Lifetime">Lifetime</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. Inform your visitor how many days the cookie will be stored or enter <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> if the cookie is a session cookie and will be deleted when the browser is closed.'=>'<translation-key id="Lifetime">Levenslang</translation-key>: dit veld komt over het algemeen overeen met de kolom <translation-key id="Expires">Vervalt</translation-key> in de sectie <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> van uw browser. Informeer uw bezoekers over de duur van de opslagperiode van de cookie of voer <translation-key id="Session">Sessie</translation-key> in als de cookie een sessiecookie is en zal worden verwijderd wanneer de browser wordt gesloten.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineIf you find a date in the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column, this means that the cookie is a persistent cookie and will be deleted on the specified date.'=>'Als u een datum vindt in de kolom <translation-key id="Expires">Vervalt</translation-key>, betekent dit dat de cookie een permanente cookie is en op de opgegeven datum wordt verwijderd.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineIf you find the value <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> in the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column of your browser, this means that the cookie is a session cookie and will be deleted when you close your browser.'=>'Als u de waarde <translation-key id="Session">Sessie</translation-key> vindt in de kolom <translation-key id="Expires">Vervalt</translation-key> van uw browser, betekent dit dat de cookie een sessiecookie is en zal worden verwijderd wanneer u uw browser afsluit.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Domain">Domain</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. You can enter <strong>#</strong> into this field and <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> will display the domain of your website in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Hostname">Hostnaam</translation-key>: dit veld komt over het algemeen overeen met de kolom <translation-key id="Domain">Domein</translation-key> in de sectie <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> van uw browser. U kunt <strong>#</strong> in dit veld invoeren en <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> zal het domein van uw website tonen in het <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-k