anslation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers-Settings">Settings</translation-key>.'=>'Algemene instellingen zijn te vinden onder <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers">Content blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers-Settings">Instellingen</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldPages to scan'=>'Pagina\'s om te scannen','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe visual appearance (colors, borders, etc.) can be customized under <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers-Appearance">Appearance</translation-key>.'=>'Het visuele uiterlijk (kleuren, randen, enz.) kan worden aangepast onder <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers">Content blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers-Appearance">Uiterlijk</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Field<translation-key id="Scan-type">Scan type</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Scan-type">Type scan</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> is active and does block content (iframes) of the configured hosts.'=>'De <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> is actief en blokkeert inhoud (iframes) van de geconfigureerde hosts.','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineSelect pages to scan'=>'Selecteer pagina\'s om te scannen','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for <transla