ebsite. For example, if the URL of the website is <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, the <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'De <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostnaam</translation-key> is de domeinnaam van de website. Als de URL van de website bijvoorbeeld <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>is, dan is de <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostnaam</translation-key> <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldCreated at'=>'Aangemaakt op','Backend / Dashboard / Alert MessageNo data available yet. Please try again in a few hours.'=>'Er zijn nog geen gegevens beschikbaar. Probeer het over een paar uur opnieuw.','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldType'=>'Type','Backend / Dashboard / BreadcrumbDashboard'=>'Dashboard','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldURLs'=>'URL\'s','Backend / Dashboard / Button Title7 Days'=>'7 dagen','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineCookies'=>'Cookies','Backend / Dashboard / Button Title30 Days'=>'30 dagen','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineExternal resources'=>'Externe bronnen','Backend / Dashboard / Button TitleToday'=>'Vandaag','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineScanned pages'=>'Gescande pagina\'s','Backend / Dashboard / Button Title30 Days by Service'=>'30 dagen per service','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineScan results'=>'Scanresultaten','Backend / Dashboard / Button TitleNo, I do not want to help'=>'Nee, ik wil niet helpen','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineSuggested Packages Already Installed'=>'Voorgestelde en reeds geïnstalleerde pakketten','Backend / Dashboard / Button Title<span class="brlbs-cmpnt-heart-icon"></span><span>Yes, I would like to help</span>'=>'<span class="brlbs-cmpnt-heart-icon"></span><span>Ja, ik wil graag helpen</span>','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineSuggested Packages to Install'=>'Voorgestelde pakketten om te installeren','Backend / Dashboard / FieldAutomatic Update'=>'Automatisch bijwerken','Backen