pakket','Backend / Dashboard / Texthere'=>'hier','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableURL'=>'URL','Backend / Dashboard / TextIn memory of Sergii Kovalenko.'=>'Ter nagedachtenis aan Sergii Kovalenko.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Textdays'=>'dagen','Backend / Dashboard / TextHelp us improve <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> by providing us with non-personal information about your website.'=>'Help ons bij het verbeteren van <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> door ons te voorzien van niet-persoonlijke informatie over uw website.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextFailed'=>'Mislukt','Backend / Dashboard / TextFor more information about what data we need and for what purpose, <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>click here</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>.'=>'<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>Klik hier</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> voor meer informatie over welke gegevens we nodig hebben en voor welk doel.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextSuccess'=>'Succesvol','Backend / Dashboard / TextThe dialog should now appear on your website. Open your website in incognito/private mode for testing. If you have any questions, please visit our <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>Knowledge Base</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>.'=>'Het dialoogvenster zou nu op uw website getoond moeten worden. Open uw website in de incognito/privé-modus om het te testen. Als u vragen heeft, bezoek dan onze <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>Kennisbank</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextScan in progress'=>'Scan bezig','Backend / Dashboard / TextPlease disable your caching plugin if it is currently enabled. Once you have completed the setup of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>, you may re-enable it.'=>'Schakel uw caching-plugin uit als deze momenteel is ingeschakeld. Wanneer u de instelling van <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> hebt voltooid, kunt u deze weer inschakelen.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextScan is analysing'=>'Scan is aan het analyseren','Backend / Dashboard / TextUpdate the default provider data under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-provider"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Providers</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Owner of this website</translation-key>. Please update the data by adding your name and address, and ensure to include the URL for the <translation-key id="Privacy-Url">Privacy URL</translation-key>.'=>'Werk de standaard providergegevens bij onder <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Toestemmingsbeheer</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-provider"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Providers</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Eigenaar van deze website</translation-key>. Werk de gegevens bij door uw naam en adres toe te voegen en voeg daarbij ook de URL voor de <translation-key id="Privacy-Url">Privacy-URL</translation-key> toe.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextScanning'=>'Scannen','Backend / Dashboard / TextClick on <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Settings">Settings</translation-key></a> and select your <translation-key id="Privacy-Page">Privacy Page</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Imprint-Page">Imprint Page</translation-key>. Add both pages to <translation-key id="Hide-Dialog-on-Pages">Hide Dialog on Pages</translation-key> too.'=>'Klik op <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialoogvenster &amp; widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Settings">Instellingen</translation-key></a> en selecteer uw <translation-key id="Privacy-Page">Privacypagina</translation-key> en <translation-key id="Imprint-Page">Afdrukpagina</translation-key>. Voeg ook beide pagina\'s toe aan <translation-key id="Hide-Dialog-on-Pages">Dialoogvenster verbergen op pagina\'s</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextSession'=>'Sessie','Backend / Dashboard / TextEnable <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> under <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Settings">Settings</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie Status</translation-key>.'=>'Schakel <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> in via <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Settings">Instellingen</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Status van Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertThe scanner\'s analysis can make suggestions for installing packages that prevent the inclusion of external resources or improve compatibility between the theme and installed plugins.'=>'De analyse van de scanner kan suggesties doen voor het installeren van pakketten, waardoor het opnemen van externe bronnen wordt voorkomen of de compatibiliteit tussen het thema en de geïnstalleerde plugins wordt verbeterd.','Backend / Dashboard / TextUse our scanner to check which cookies are set on your website and which services are used. Click on <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-cloud-scan"><translation-key id="Navigation-Scanner">Scanner</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Button-Add-New">Add New</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Button-Create-Scan">Create scan</translation-key> to add a new scan job. The <translation-key id="Scan-type">Scan type</translation-key> should be set to <translation-key id="Setup">Setup</translation-key>. '=>'Gebruik onze scanner om te controleren welke cookies zijn ingesteld op uw website en welke services er worden gebruikt. Klik op <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-cloud-scan"><translation-key id="Navigation-Scanner">Scanner</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Button-Add-New">Nieuwe toevoegen</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Button-Create-Scan">Scan aanmaken</translation-key> om een nieuwe scantaak toe te voegen. De <translation-key id="Scan-type">Type scan</translation-key> moet worden ingesteld op <translation-key id="Setup">Instelling</translation-key>. ','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertClick on the <translation-key id="Button-Details">Details</translation-key> button to get more information about the package. Once the package is installed, you will be redirected back to this page to proceed with the installation of the next package.'=>'Klik op de knop <translation-key id="Button-Details">Details</translation-key> voor meer informatie over het pakket. Zodra het pakket is geïnstalleerd, wordt u teruggeleid naar deze pagina om verder te gaan met de installatie van het volgende pakket.','Backend / Dashboard / TextAfter you have used the scanner and installed suggested packages, create a new scan job and set <translation-key id="Scan-type">Scan type</translation-key> to <translation-key id="Audit">Audit</translation-key>. This scan type is used to verify that your website does not load cookies or external resources without obtaining the appropriate consent.'=>'Nadat u de scanner hebt gebruikt en de voorgestelde pakketten hebt geïnstalleerd, maakt u een nieuwe scantaak aan en stelt u <translation-key id="Scan-type">Type scan</translation-key> in op <translation-key id="Audit">Audit</translation-key>. Dit type scan wordt gebruikt om te controleren of uw website geen cookies of externe bronnen laadt zonder daarvoor de juiste toestemming te hebben.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipTo comply with data protection, cookies must be blocked in most cases until consent is given. Only essential cookies may be set without consent. An essential cookie could be one that, for instance, stores the shopping cart contents or the selected language.'=>'Om te voldoen aan de gegevensbescherming moeten cookies meestal worden geblokkeerd totdat er toestemming is gegeven. Alleen essentiële cookies mogen zonder toestemming worden geplaatst. Een essentiële cookie kan bijvoorbeeld een cookie zijn die de inhoud van het winkelwagentje of de geselecteerde taal opslaat.','Backend / Dashboard / TextExplore our <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-library"><translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key></a> to have an overview of all our available packages. Here you can find templates for <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> (e.g. Google Analytics) or <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> (e.g. YouTube) and much more.'=>'Ontdek onze <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-library"><translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Bibliotheek</translation-key></a> voor een overzicht van al onze beschikbare pakketten. U vindt hier sjablonen voor <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> (bijv. Google Analytics) of <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content blockers</translation-key> (bijv. YouTube) en nog veel meer.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipClick the icon to view sample locations associated with the detected cookie.'=>'Klik op het pictogram om voorbeeldadressen te tonen die aan het gedetecteerde cookie zijn gekoppeld.','Backend / Dashboard / TextIf you place ads on your website, you may need to enable the IAB TCF under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-iab-tcf-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF-Settings">Settings</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF Status</translation-key>. And then configure vendors under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-iab-tcf-vendor"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF-Manage-Vendors">Manage Vendors</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Configure-Vendors">Configure Vendors</translation-key>.'=>'Als u advertenties op uw website plaatst, moet u mogelijk het IAB TCF inschakelen via <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Toestemmingsbeheer</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-iab-tcf-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF-Settings">Instellingen</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF-status</translation-key>. Configureer vervolgens de verkopers via <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Toestemmingsbeheer</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-iab-tcf-vendor"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF-Manage-Vendors">Verkopers beheren</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Configure-Vendors">Verkopers configureren</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Suggested package</translation-key>: This column lists a recommended package to install to block the cookie if the cookie is not essential.'=>'<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Aanbevolen pakket</translation-key>: in deze kolom staat een aanbevolen pakket om te installeren om de cookie te blokkeren indien de cookie niet essentieel is.','Backend / Dashboard / TextYou can customize the dialog texts under <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-localization"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Localization">Localization</translation-key></a>. The visual appearance (colors, spacing, etc.) can be customized under <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-appearance"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Appearance">Appearance</translation-key></a>. Everything else like layout, position, buttons, etc. you can define under <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Settings">Settings</translation-key></a>.'=>'U kunt de teksten van dialoogvensters aanpassen via <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialoogvenster &amp; widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-localization"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Localization">Lokalisatie</translation-key></a>. Het visuele uiterlijk (kleuren, spatiëring, enz.) kan worden aangepast via <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialoogvenster &amp; widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-appearance"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Appearance">Uiterlijk</translation-key></a>. U kunt al het overige, zoals lay-out, positie, knoppen, enz. instellen via <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialoogvenster &amp; widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialoogvenster</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Settings">Instellingen</translation-key></a>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipCookies'=>'Cookies','Backend / Dashboard / TextThank you!'=>'Bedankt!','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipExternal resources'=>'Externe bronnen','Backend / Dashboard / URLhttps://borlabs.io/borlabs-cookie/telemetry/'=>'https://borlabs.io/borlabs-cookie/telemetry/','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Dashboard / URLhttps://borlabs.io/support/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&utm_medium=Dashboard+Link&utm_campaign=Analysis'=>'https://borlabs.io/support/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&utm_medium=Dashboard+Link&utm_campaign=Analysis','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipExternal resources are resources that are loaded from a different domain than the page itself. For example, if you have a page with the URL <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong> and this page loads a resource from <strong><em>https://www.example.org</em></strong>, then this resource is considered an external resource. To comply with data protection, in most cases, these external resources must be blocked until consent is given.'=>'Externe bronnen zijn bronnen die worden geladen vanaf een ander domein dan de pagina zelf. Als u bijvoorbeeld een pagina hebt met de URL <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong> en deze pagina een bron laadt van <strong><em>https://www.example.org</em></strong>, dan wordt deze bron beschouwd als een externe bron. Om de gegevensbescherming na te leven, moeten deze externe bronnen meestal worden geblokkeerd totdat er toestemming is gegeven.','Seeder / Default Content Blocker / DescriptionThe <strong><em>Default</em> Content Blocker</strong> is a special type that is always used when no specific <strong>Content Blocker</strong> was found.<br>Therefore it is not possible to use the <strong>Unblock all</strong> feature.'=>'De <strong><em>standaard</em> content blocker</strong> is een speciaal type dat altijd wordt gebruikt als er geen specifieke <strong>content blocker</strong> is gevonden.<br>Daarom is het niet mogelijk om de functie <strong>alles deblokkeren</strong> te gebruiken.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipClick on the icon to get detailed information about the external resource. In the details you can find examples of discovered resources and their respective locations.'=>'Klik op het pictogram om gedetailleerde informatie over de externe bron te krijgen. In de details leest u meer over voorbeelden van ontdekte bronnen en hun respectievelijke adressen.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="External-hostname">External hostname</translation-key>: Resources are being loaded from this source.'=>'<translation-key id="External-hostname">Externe hostnaam</translation-key>: bronnen worden van deze bron geladen.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Number-of-resources">Number of resources</translation-key>: The number of resources loaded from this source. The resources found are limited to 10 per hostname.'=>'<translation-key id="Number-of-resources">Aantal bronnen</translation-key>: het aantal bronnen dat van deze bron is geladen. De gevonden bronnen zijn beperkt tot 10 per hostnaam.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Suggested package</translation-key>: This column lists a recommended package to install to block the external resource.'=>'<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Aanbevolen pakket</translation-key>: in deze kolom staat een aanbevolen pakket om te installeren voor het blokkeren van de externe bron.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipFailed: The scanner could not scan the page. More information can be found in the <translation-key id="Failure-type">Failure type</translation-key> column.'=>'Mislukt: de scanner kon de pagina niet scannen. U vindt meer informatie in de kolom <translation-key id="Failure-type">Type fout</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipSuccess: The page was scanned successfully.'=>'Succesvol: de pagina is succesvol gescand.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipScanning: The page is being scanned.'=>'Scannen: de pagina wordt gescand.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertNo <translation-key id="Scans">Scans</translation-key> configured.'=>'Er zijn geen <translation-key id="Scans">Scans</translation-key> geconfigureerd.','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineScanner'=>'Scanner','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableCloud Scan ID'=>'Cloud scan-ID','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableCreated at'=>'Aangemaakt op','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableScanned pages'=>'Gescande pagina\'s','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableType'=>'Type','Backend / Cloud Scan / Things to know / TextThe s